rows.label: tlk401005_msg0001
rows.name:
There was one request I thought
was decidedly suspicious.

rows.label: tlk401005_msg0002
rows.name:
We had a Nopon fellow asking about
supplies of poisonous substances.

rows.label: tlk401005_msg0003
rows.name:
I told him we do not handle such items
here, of course, and he left soon after.

rows.label: tlk401005_msg0004
rows.name:
But from what I hear, he's been
asking around other places too.

rows.label: tlk401005_msg0005
rows.name: Who knows what he might be plotting?
